{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":583880,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":121506,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re : 前提是你别网络暴力别人","timestamp":1605830262,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":583889,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":121506,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"所以所谓的宽容，只是为自己将来的犯错留下余地罢了。","timestamp":1605830446,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":583890,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":121506,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"我觉得学弟就是大家的快乐工具人，学弟要什么已经不重要了，大家发泄爽了就好","timestamp":1605830483,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":583907,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":121506,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"我也在想这个问题，不能让恶传递，这不是基本的文明社会的做法吗","timestamp":1605830985,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":583911,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":121506,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"以直报怨，以德报德，没啥问题","timestamp":1605831052,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":583914,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Francis","permissions":["report"],"pid":121506,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"前提是，你在没看监控的情况下挂学弟的时候，考虑过给他造成了社死吗","timestamp":1605831166,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":583920,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Grace","permissions":["report"],"pid":121506,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"嗨呀，是靖靖吗？","timestamp":1605831309,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":583948,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Hans","permissions":["report"],"pid":121506,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"学姐好呀","timestamp":1605831958,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":583979,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Isabella","permissions":["report"],"pid":121506,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Dave: 你走在路上，被路上的石头绊了一跤。更确切地说，你还离它三米远呢，那石头就飞到你脚下把你绊倒了。你会怎么做？爬起来把石头扔到路边防止它再绊人不是很正常的吗？\n你只看到了惩罚的暴力性，却没看到惩罚所制止的、更大的暴力 。","timestamp":1605832856,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":583990,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Jason","permissions":["report"],"pid":121506,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"捅了别人一刀被捅一刀，我觉得合理。感性上，别问怎么衡量一刀，我也没想明白","timestamp":1605833142,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":584027,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Kate","permissions":["report"],"pid":121506,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Isabella: 不妨碍我把石头扔粪坑里","timestamp":1605833800,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":584044,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Louis","permissions":["report"],"pid":121506,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"当然希望 凭什么她污蔑别人还能安然无恙","timestamp":1605834071,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":584069,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Margaret","permissions":["report"],"pid":121506,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"插着腰让别人要大度点的，要离他远一点，不然雷劈他的时候会连累到你","timestamp":1605834630,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":584083,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Nathan","permissions":["report"],"pid":121506,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"犯错了还不应该受到惩罚？等哪天你遇到了 ，千万别让暴力传播哦！","timestamp":1605834822,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":584157,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Olivia","permissions":["report"],"pid":121506,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"围观的各位没有任何资格去惩罚或者下定义","timestamp":1605835556,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":592444,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Francis","permissions":["report"],"pid":121506,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Olivia: 你有什么资格为她洗地？","timestamp":1605926922,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":12,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":121506,"reply":16,"tag":null,"text":"真的有那么多我校同学希望那位女生被网络暴力作为惩罚吗？当一个人捅别人一刀，就该被捅十刀作为惩罚，用暴力惩罚暴力，这是合理的吗？\n那人就一辈子不要犯错，犯了错就该死\n","timestamp":1605829033,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782653,"url":"","vote":{}}}